      "description": "Arithmetic sequences (Tn = a + (n−1)d, Sn = n/2[2a + (n−1)d]). Geometric sequences (Tn = ar^(n−1), Sn = a(r^n − 1)/(r − 1)). Sum to infinity S∞ = a/(1−r) for |r|<1. Sigma notation. Proof by induction (enrichment)",
